- What time would you like to have dinner?
- What is the name of the restaurant where you would like to reserve a table?
- How many people will be attending the dinner (including yourself, Alice, and Bob)?

For setting up the calendar event, I will need the date and time of the dinner, which will be available once the reservation is made.

Once I have this information, I will proceed to:
1. Visit www.cs_conference.com to check your conference registration details.
2. Visit www.dinnerreservations.com to reserve a dinner table.
3. Set up a calendar event for the dinner with Alice and Bob.
